If feeling blue looked like this 🙈

#gifted #notsponsored 

I received these Kajal/eyeshadow sticks and the minute I opened the package and saw the metallic blue shade. I knew that this is what I wanted to recreate. 

It’s from @simplynam.beauty 

Their viral Kajal which is available in 4 shades and trust me the color from the waterline didn’t budge which is a win for me! 🙌🏼 

The shades blended really well to create this look and the application was very smooth too. 

Shades used: 
🤎Metallic Bronze 
♠️ Ink Black 
🦋 Metallic Blue
